atures ($T$), and we find that there is a dramatic\nincreasing trend of $T$ with increasing $L_{IR}^{(cd)}$. We interpret this\ntrend as the envelope of the general distribution of infrared galaxies on the\n($T$, $L_{IR}^{(cd)}$) plane.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Jan 2015 17:15:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Aug 2015 07:29:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-30"}
