\nsuggestion that the weak velocity field usually observed in dense clumps and\nsmaller cores is likely seeded by the growth of dynamic instabilities.\nSimulations were performed using the smooth particle hydrodynamics algorithm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Jan 2015 09:06:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
