 if light is allowed to travel\nthrough several structures instead of just one.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Jan 2015 09:39:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 15 Feb 2015 16:49:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 15 Aug 2015 08:07:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-18"}
