parent windows, autotrigger electronics and studying the cluster\nshape at different energies. As a high flux of axion-like-particles is expected\nin this energy range, a sub-keV threshold detector could enlarge the physics\ncase of axion helioscopes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Jan 2015 12:29:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-01-08"}
